Creative nails are the best accessory!

Hannah Lee, creator of the popular YouTube Channel Hannah Rox Nails, shares more than thirty new nail designs in Cool Nail Art. With tips on how to prep your manicure, clear step-by-step instructions and easy-to-use tools, you can create fabulous nail art designs in your own home.

Learn easy techniques, including dotting, decals, taping, striping and gradients.
Choose from thirty-five great designs or try one of the many variations.
Learn how to adapt designs for your toes for a complete look.
Create designs using at-home items like toothpicks and painter's tape.
